{"tid":1008066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛回家] 如何檢舉翻牆的中國網民？這招幫助他們找到回家的路","createTime":"2019-02-04T08:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T04:38:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":99,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5c617f3d206d45c20de239109f01f75d9a8a3466","tid":1008066,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:12:00.000Z","msg":"如何檢舉翻牆的中國網民？這招幫助他們找到回家的路<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zi.media/@hugo3c/post/wUUnmQ?fbclid=IwAR2rP60ce1fbmFn2u4QJgtQkk3cVU9VuLtQgxQD-B1bBuCt4cFXmYCPljAI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzi.media%2F%40hugo3c%2Fpost%2FwUUnmQ%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2rP60ce1fbmFn2u4QJgtQkk3cVU9VuLtQgxQD-B1bBuCt4cFXmYCPljAI&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ5a4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=512b556e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zi.media/@hugo3c/post/wUUnmQ?fbclid=IwAR2rP60ce1fbmFn2u4QJgtQkk3cVU9VuLtQgxQD-B1bBuCt4cFXmYCPljAI</a><br />\n<br />\n常常在臉書、YouTube 上看到各種從大陸翻牆過來的網友，發表各種侵略性的言論嗎？現在有方法可以「回敬」他們了，而且是 100% 合法的方式，利用中國的中央網信辦 (國家互聯網信息辦公室)，檢舉違法利用 VPN 等翻牆軟體過來的民眾，將留言截圖 (越多越好)，就可以請這些網民「回家」吃自己啦！<br />\n<br />\n國家互聯網信息辦公室：<a href=\"http://www.12377.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.12377.cn%2F&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ5a4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=f682f250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.12377.cn/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-0&h=30091da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 點擊上方連結進入中央網信辦，點擊「違法和不良信息舉報入口」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-1&h=88b57acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 接著會有個舉報須知，大概看一下就好 XD 不過看完滑到最下面有個同意需要按一下才能繼續下一步。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-2&h=9a00d522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 舉報分類選擇「其它」類。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-3&h=22bcb247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 接著點擊「匿名用戶舉報」，舉報平台選擇「客戶端 APP」，將 APP 名稱打上，並將 APP 官方的網址也貼上，最後舉報內容填寫違反使用 VPN 等類似陳述即可，因為最重要的截圖，有越多截圖越好，點擊「請選擇附件」來上傳，最後輸入驗證碼後按下繼續舉報即可。另外，同樣重要的是，請將繁體字通通都轉成簡體字，繁轉簡傳送門也準備好啦～舉報成功後會收到一組查詢碼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-4&h=bf6b8afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 未來可以在同一個平台上查詢舉報處理進度！是不是覺得很新奇 XD 大家如果遇到翻牆網民來挑釁，就用這招回敬吧！學起來了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fe8d61bdbb82046faf9560f063cbde460fdc54","tid":1008066,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645972333f837814e15c4cc1e1329526711ca29b","tid":1008066,"uid":3457,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:13:56.000Z","msg":"檢舉翻牆有冇錢收 有既全職做"},{"pid":"3612c124de89d61fe6bc6cca60439767d7e0e13f","tid":1008066,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"職員要翻牆去調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326cd903f8e6cf3af3263d32c03f1e926c1ae6b3","tid":1008066,"uid":25468,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:16:16.000Z","msg":"有新聞講左 99% 支那翻牆APP 係中共背後控制 , 投訴條毛咩"},{"pid":"fff8298d74218156e651a5672976f8c2474f948a","tid":1008066,"uid":173227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:18:15.000Z","msg":"一大班共匪攞正牌翻牆檢都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢度都一大班"},{"pid":"c0cf12799b9066fcf23742965275553f16515414","tid":1008