.com.hk/article/2266426/VPN%20%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E7%9B%B4%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9F%E8%A9%95%E6%B8%AC%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%2086%EF%BC%85%20%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%20VPN%20apps%20%E5%AD%98%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E9%9A%B1%E6%86%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2266426%2FVPN%2520%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E7%2589%2586%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25EF%25BC%259F%25E8%25A9%2595%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%252086%25EF%25BC%2585%2520%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%2520VPN%2520apps%2520%25E5%25AD%2598%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25E9%259A%25B1%25E6%2586%2582&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ5a4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=2955e9f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2266426/VPN%20%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E7%9B%B4%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9F%E8%A9%95%E6%B8%AC%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%2086%EF%BC%85%20%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%20VPN%20apps%20%E5%AD%98%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E9%9A%B1%E6%86%82</a><br />\n-------------------------------<br />\n測試左所有 app 共 30款 , 59%同中國有關 , 即係大約 18款app<br />\n而結論有 59%（18 款）apps 跟中國大陸有聯繫"},{"pid":"244e9314fb6b1e1eef137bc3054188d000891d99","tid":1008066,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"645972333f837814e15c4cc1e1329526711ca29b","tid":1008066,"uid":3457,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:13:56.000Z","msg":"檢舉翻牆有冇錢收 有既全職做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"積陰德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395a42f0e225b863962daeecdaeb9f66ec3a6479","tid":1008066,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"支國舉報人好像要提供實名同中國身分證先得喎<br />\n